{"tid":616635,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"中國內地基督教教堂公約：九個不准","createTime":"2018-04-04T10:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T10:33:50.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b6cb5512486108d3cc2bae93d78a06a455e86302","tid":616635,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:27:07.000Z","msg":"1 不允許18歲以下兒童入教堂<br />\n2 不允許共產黨員非工作原因入教堂<br />\n3 不允許未經兩會批准接待外來講員<br />\n4 不允許宗教活動場所外，開展任何宗教活動（包括傳教、探訪）<br />\n5 不允許非法傳播及經營宗教書籍、刊物及宗教用品<br />\n6 不允許到未經批准的場所活動<br />\n7 不允許網上非法傳播宗教內容的文字圖片<br />\n8 不允許在街道或路邊設置宗教色彩的標牌<br />\n9 不允許未經批准舉辦培訓班<br />\n<br />\n摘自：中國河南省南陽市淅川縣基督教三自愛國委員會， 2018年3月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/181631_80a32532f2f5711a216fb6bb9fb17714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F181631_80a32532f2f5711a216fb6bb9fb17714.jpg&h=40598615&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b20c751cb4772460a2e70d3c13a8760594e003f","tid":616635,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"091ea849305e31cdcb2914c6a3380f8c4e30d510","tid":616635,"uid":174502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:32:23.000Z","msg":"你以為基督就唔使愛党啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb5b6fa0437aaa94c9c4b99a36f94048124f561","tid":616635,"uid":54046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b20c751cb4772460a2e70d3c13a8760594e003f","tid":616635,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T10:33:50.000Z","msg":"回教仲勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}